reference "fig:Breakdown-of-downtime"

\end_inset

 presents breakdown of dead-time to reaction time (time between problem
 occurrence and recovery action taken) and recovery time (time between recovery
 action start and end).
 Reducing both reaction time and choosing correct optimal recovery action
 are the two areas for improvement.
\end_layout

