LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Breakdown-of-downtime"

\end_inset

, the time spent on recovery, is the main contributor to overall downtime
 of CMS.
 Therefore its essential to choose the quickest set of actions needed to
 bring the system back to operation.
 Many different recovery procedures may be distinguished, for example:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
stop the run and start
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
reconfigure specific subsystem
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
red and green recycle
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
